msg: Added CIFSUser implementation by Doug Chestnut and Peter Shipley. This allows to authenticate users against CIFS using JCIFS. Lenya ships with a mock jar, replace with the real thing if you want to use this. This resolves http://issues.apache.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=27289
